Steven Carl Day was allegedly murdered on December 18, 2013 in Grand Rapids, Michigan . 
  Robert Mccombs told a court that Day admitted to him and his roommate Roger Musick that he molested a young relative and that he thought 'one of them was starting to like it' Day was strangled to death by Musick . 
  Day and Musick were charged with tampering with evidence but later released . 
 